          <p class='first-para'>
            Before the Minister leaves the subject of charges, can he tell us whether a parallel exercise of containing charges has taken place in Scotland and the level of the charges that he expects to be applied there?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0354P1-05493'>
        <a name='S6CV0354P1_20000720_WH_29'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-meacher' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
